        "subject": "LU-4821 tests: clean up get_mds_num to be get_mdt_idx",
        "message": "LU-4821 tests: clean up get_mds_num to be get_mdt_idx\n\nThe get_mds_num() helper function returned the MDS facet number\ninstead of the MDT index, but it is actually more useful if it\nreturns the MDT index, since this can be extracted directly\nfrom a file via \"lfs getdirstripe -M\".\n\nRename the function and fix the few callers to use get_mdt_idx().\n\nFix some coding style issues in the affected functions.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I23d6b4c8da6e50ee1d94cf7be455265bbf3ebbe5\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
